  "detailed_description": "This is a Mahjong game from china.It is not four people game that is traditional chinese Mahjong game ,but it is two people game . <br />\r\nThis game has two mode:local game mode and network game mode.in local game mode,player will get coins by a virtual competitor and player's level up.<br />\r\nin network game mode,player will play Mahjong game with another player from internet.<br />\r\nIf you wanna learn play Mahjong ,And this game will make you become an expert .",
